<td><span style="font-size: 10pt;">None.<br/> </span></td>
<td><p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Salary sacrifice arrangements<b> </b>must be evidenced using one of the following options:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 10pt;">a payslip or</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 10pt;">a letter/statement from the employer or salary sacrfice provider outlining the details of the salary sacrifice arrangement.</span></li>
</ul> <p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Where there are multiple salary sacrifice deductions, and they are not itemised on the payslip, additional documents (e.g. a letter/statement from the salary sacrifice provider outlining the details of the salary sacrifice arrangement) must be provided</span></p> </td>
<td><span style="font-size: 10pt;">100%<br/> </span></td>
